Citation.sAbstract: The bubble points for (triethyl orthoformate + diethyl malonate) at the temperatures T = 373.15 K, 383.15 K, 393.15 K and at the pressure p = 13.33 kPa, measured with an inclined ebulliometer are presented. The experimental results are analyzed using the UNIQUAC equation with the temperature-dependent binary parameters with satisfactory results. Experimental vapour pressures of triethyl orthoformate are also included.
Citation.sTitle: Bubble points measurement for (triethyl orthoformate + diethyl malonate)
